
Wed Sep 6 2023

   --sam

      Option to set relevant parameters for sam format processing.

      (1) sets -kO11
      (2) recognises sam headers and reads sequence lengths into the dictionary called 'seqlen'.

      The lenght of a sequence can be retrieved in a computation, e.g. with

      pick --sam rlen::3^seqlen,map

      (--sam existed before; that functionality is now available with --rmm sam, see below).

   --remind-me <ofthis>
   --rmm <ofthis>

      New option; e.g. --rmm sam prints a short description of sam format.

